{"type": "article", "id": 21293, "title": "带荧光黄和橙红色的文具系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-26T08:23:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122306fwr5mCIcYOA3zUWq.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利文具品牌 Moleskine、欧洲设计公司 Driade 和法国设计师 Philippe Nigro 合作推出了这一系列家具 Portable Atelier，包括桌子、凳子和桌面文具。他们使用了橡木、胶合板和钢材，整体是浅棕色和黑色的搭配，很简洁。但在桌面文具上使用了橙红色和荧光黄，立刻打破了原本有些沉闷的搭配，赋予了活泼和潮流的气质。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150852aOEYFPAmQBtH7jwC.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"662\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150853WM3qh7taPclHV5KS.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"662\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150853IztN2TPFk1LKnopv.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"662\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150853asbiOpR65cXGvQVg.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"662\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}